    <h1>Bertazzoni Oven Repair in Los Angeles</h1>
    <p class="lede">Bertazzoni is the independent Italian family-owned luxury appliance brand (Guastalla, Reggio Emilia, since 1882, sixth-generation Bertazzoni family ownership — notably NOT part of Middleby/BSH/Samsung/Whirlpool/Electrolux conglomerate structure). Our LA Bertazzoni oven service covers the built-in lineup: <b>Professional Series</b> flagship (pro-style stainless, Convection Steam option, 60+ color-panel program, Brass knob option), <b>Master Series</b> mid-tier (standard features, restrained styling), and <b>Heritage Series</b> legacy (2005-2018 builds still in service fleet). Product formats include standard built-in convection, <b>Convection Steam Oven</b> (Professional-only hybrid with dedicated GSC demand), and matched-range oven service where the Professional built-in oven is specified alongside a Professional Series range. Italian color-panel service + Convection Steam descaling + Englewood Cliffs NJ parts chain are the Bertazzoni-specific skill areas. Same-day dispatch. $89 residential diagnostic, waived with repair.</p>
